\begin_layout Enumerate
Is the set open? Closed?
\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 is not open because the point 
\begin_inset Formula $1=(-1)^{1}+\frac{2}{1}\in A$
\end_inset

 does not have an 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon$
\end_inset

-neighborhood contained entirely within 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

.
 
\begin_inset Formula $A$
\end_inset

 is not closed because the limit point 
\begin_inset Formula $-1$
\end_inset

