\begin_layout Enumerate
\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

 is open because every 
\begin_inset Formula $x\in B$
\end_inset

 has an 
\begin_inset Formula $\epsilon$
\end_inset

-neighborhood of radius 
\begin_inset Formula $\min\{1-x,x\}$
\end_inset

