\begin_inset Formula $B$
\end_inset

, 
\begin_inset Formula $0$
\end_inset

 and 
\begin_inset Formula $1$
\end_inset

, are not contained in the set.
 Therefore, 
\begin_inset Formula $\bar{B}=B\cup\{0,1\}$
\end_inset

.
\end_layout

\end_deeper
