\end_layout

\begin_deeper
\begin_layout Standard
True.
 Suppose that 
\begin_inset Formula $g(f(x_{1}))=g(f(x_{2}))$
\end_inset

.
 Then, since 
\begin_inset Formula $g$
\end_inset

